songs.title: ​​Old Town Road (Troop Remix)*
songs.lyrics:
Lyrics From Snippet

(Kio, Kio)
I got my troops, they in the back
They ready to attack
AK is attached
And the scope is black to match
Ridin' on a tank, ha
Smoking on that dank
Just copped a Camaro
Now I'm headed to the bank
Can't nobody tell we comin'
